---
<!-- Steps Section -->
<section id="steps" class="steps section">

  <!-- Section Title -->
  <div class="container section-title" data-aos="fade-up">
    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <div><span>How Green Orbit Space</span> <span class="description-title">Delivers Value</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">

    <div class="steps-wrapper">

      <!-- Step 01 -->
      <div class="step-item" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-binoculars"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <span class="step-number">Step 01</span>
            <h3>Discovery & Listening</h3>
            <p>We begin by understanding your mission, stakeholders, and communications environment. This includes audience research, media landscape analysis, and assessment of organisational objectives. Insight ensures every message is credible, compelling, and aligned with your purpose.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 02 -->
      <div class="step-item" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-pencil-square"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <span class="step-number">Step 02</span>
            <h3>Strategy & Storytelling</h3>
            <p>We craft communication strategies and narrative frameworks that translate complex space missions into meaningful stories. From campaigns and PR to stakeholder engagement, every output is designed to enhance visibility, credibility, and impact across diverse channels.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 03 -->
      <div class="step-item" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="400">
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-megaphone-fill"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <span class="step-number">Step 03</span>
            <h3>Implementation & Engagement</h3>
            <p>We deliver campaigns, events, media outreach, and digital communications that amplify your mission. Collaboration, agility, and attention to stakeholder needs ensure messages resonate, fostering trust, engagement, and long-term impact.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 04 -->
      <div class="step-item" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="500">
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-stars"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <span class="step-number">Step 04</span>
            <h3>Review, Learn & Amplify</h3>
            <p>We monitor performance, gather feedback, and optimise communications strategies to enhance reach and impact. Learning cycles, measurement, and adaptive storytelling ensure your organisationâ€™s mission continues to inspire, educate, and engage audiences globally.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>